        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:25:26 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:25:26 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/fast-moving-southern-california-wildfire-torches-hillside-homes-forcing-evacuations.webp" alt="Fast-moving Southern California wildfire torches hillside homes, forcing evacuations"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fast-moving Southern California wildfire torches hillside homes, forcing evacuations</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAN BERNARDINO, Calif. (AP) — A fast-moving wildfire that swept into a Southern California hillside community this week destroyed five homes and damaged three others, authorities said Tuesday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/fast-moving-southern-california-wildfire-torches-hillside-homes-forcing-evacuations/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:26:37 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 13:26:37 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Seung Min Kim, KTLA 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/who-is-tim-walz-harris-picks-minnesota-gov-as-running-mate.webp" alt="Who is Tim Walz? Harris picks Minnesota gov. as running mate"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Who is Tim Walz? Harris picks Minnesota gov. as running mate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Kamala Harris picked Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz to be her running mate on Tuesday, according to three people who spoke to The Associated Press on condition of anonymity.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/who-is-tim-walz-harris-picks-minnesota-gov-as-running-mate/"  >(Seung Min Kim, KTLA 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:17:32 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:17:32 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/kamala-harris-tim-walz-to-appear-at-first-rally-as-running-mates.webp" alt="Harris introduces new running mate Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz as the 'vice president America deserves'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris introduces new running mate Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz as the 'vice president America deserves'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Kamala Harris and Minnesota Governor Tim Walz are scheduled to take the stage together at a rally in Philadelphia Tuesday night, marking their first campaign appearance together since becoming running mates.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/kamala-harris-tim-walz-to-appear-at-first-rally-as-running-mates/"  >(The Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:20:39 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:20:39 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/unclaimed-navy-veteran-laid-rest-presence-community.webp" alt="Unclaimed Navy veteran to be laid to rest in presence of community"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Unclaimed Navy veteran to be laid to rest in presence of community</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The general public is encouraged to attend the funeral services and burial of an unclaimed Navy veteran who was honorably discharged in 1977.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/unclaimed-navy-veteran-laid-rest-presence-community/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:52:14 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:52:14 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARCIA DUNN, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/nasa-delays-next-crew-launch-to-buy-more-time-at-the-space-station-for-boeings-troubled-capsule.webp" alt="NASA delays next crew launch to buy more time at the space station for Boeing's troubled capsule"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NASA delays next crew launch to buy more time at the space station for Boeing's troubled capsule</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NASA is delaying its next astronaut launch to buy more time at the International Space Station for Boeing’s troubled new crew capsule. The space agency said Tuesday it’s bumping SpaceX’s four-person flight from this month to next. It’s now targeted for Sept. 24 at the earliest.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/nasa-delays-next-crew-launch-to-buy-more-time-at-the-space-station-for-boeings-troubled-capsule/"  >(MARCIA DUNN, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:57:14 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:57:14 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Austin Turner, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/police-find-hideout-with-stolen-goods-inside-former-california-marine-corps-hangar.webp" alt="Police find hideout with stolen goods inside former California Marine Corps hangar"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Police find hideout with stolen goods inside former California Marine Corps hangar</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Police were performing what authorities called a "proactive check" on a former Marine Corps air station Friday in Irvine, California when they found a makeshift living space containing a large cache of allegedly stolen items.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/police-find-hideout-with-stolen-goods-inside-former-california-marine-corps-hangar/"  >(Austin Turner, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:20:57 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:20:57 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Addy Bink, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/06/cash-app-settlement-are-you-eligible-to-claim-up-to-2500.webp" alt="Cash App settlement: Are you eligible to claim up to $2,500?"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cash App settlement: Are you eligible to claim up to $2,500?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The lawsuit accuses Cash App and its parent company of negligence after some account data was accessed by unauthorized users.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/06/cash-app-settlement-are-you-eligible-to-claim-up-to-2500/"  >(Addy Bink, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
