        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:54:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:54:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/05/bangladesh-pm-hasina-resignation-india.webp" alt="Bangladesh's PM resigns after nearly 100 killed in weekend clashes"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bangladesh's PM resigns after nearly 100 killed in weekend clashes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Bangladesh Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina fled to India on Monday shortly after resigning from her post, following weeks of unrest in the South Asian nation that culminated in nearly 100 deaths in clashes this weekend.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/05/bangladesh-pm-hasina-resignation-india/"  >(Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:35:03 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:35:03 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/05/north-korean-leader-marks-the-delivery-of-250-nuclear-capable-missile-launchers-to-frontline-units.webp" alt="North Korean leader marks the delivery of 250 nuclear-capable missile launchers to frontline units"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">North Korean leader marks the delivery of 250 nuclear-capable missile launchers to frontline units</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SEOUL, South Korea (AP) — North Korea marked the delivery of 250 nuclear-capable missile launchers to frontline military units at a ceremony where leader Kim Jong Un called for a ceaseless expansion of his military's nuclear program to counter perceived U.S. threats, state media said Monday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/05/north-korean-leader-marks-the-delivery-of-250-nuclear-capable-missile-launchers-to-frontline-units/"  >(KIM TONG-HYUNG, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:55:14 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:55:14 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/04/scottie-scheffler-wins-olympic-gold-medal-in-golf-thriller.webp" alt="Scottie Scheffler wins Olympic gold medal in golf thriller"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Scottie Scheffler wins Olympic gold medal in golf thriller</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Scheffler becomes the second straight American to win gold in men's golf, following Xander Schauffele in the Tokyo Games.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/04/scottie-scheffler-wins-olympic-gold-medal-in-golf-thriller/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:16:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:16:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/06/israel-hamas-war-latest-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-as-world-leaders-try-to-avoid-regional-war.webp" alt="Israel-Hamas war latest: Hamas chooses Oct. 7 mastermind as their new leader as wider war feared"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israel-Hamas war latest: Hamas chooses Oct. 7 mastermind as their new leader as wider war feared</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Palestinian militant group Hamas said Tuesday it has chosen Yahya Sinwar, its top official in Gaza who masterminded the Oct. 7 attacks in Israel, as its new leader.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/06/israel-hamas-war-latest-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-as-world-leaders-try-to-avoid-regional-war/"  >(The Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:39:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:39:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JAMEY KEATEN, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/07/31/un-report-says-palestinians-detained-by-israeli-authorities-since-oct-7-faced-torture-mistreatment.webp" alt="UN report says Palestinians detained by Israeli authorities since Oct. 7 faced torture, mistreatment"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">UN report says Palestinians detained by Israeli authorities since Oct. 7 faced torture, mistreatment</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      GENEVA (AP) — The U.N. human rights office issued a report Wednesday saying Palestinians detained by Israeli authorities since the Oct. 7 attacks faced waterboarding, sleep deprivation, electric shocks, dogs set on them, and other forms of torture and mistreatment.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/07/31/un-report-says-palestinians-detained-by-israeli-authorities-since-oct-7-faced-torture-mistreatment/"  >(JAMEY KEATEN, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:42:13 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 05:42:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="LLAZAR SEMINI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/05/albanias-governing-socialist-party-wins-mayoral-poll-in-a-town-with-ethnic-greek-minority.webp" alt="Albania's governing Socialist Party wins mayoral poll in a town with ethnic Greek minority"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Albania's governing Socialist Party wins mayoral poll in a town with ethnic Greek minority</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      QEPARO, Albania (AP) — Preliminary results Monday showed Albania's governing Socialist Party candidate Vangjel Tavo won the mayoral election in the southwestern town of Himara after the previous mayor was removed in a case that has sparked tensions with Greece.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/05/albanias-governing-socialist-party-wins-mayoral-poll-in-a-town-with-ethnic-greek-minority/"  >(LLAZAR SEMINI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:40:22 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:40:22 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SOPHENG CHEANG and ANIRUDDHA GHOSAL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/05/cambodia-breaks-ground-on-china-funded-canal-and-says-it-will-be-built-no-matter-the-cost.webp" alt="Cambodia breaks ground on China-funded canal and says it will be built 'no matter the cost'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cambodia breaks ground on China-funded canal and says it will be built 'no matter the cost'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PREK TAKEO, Cambodia (AP) — Cambodia broke ground Monday on a controversial, China-funded canal to link the capital Phnom Penh to the sea, despite environmental concerns and the risk of straining ties with neighboring Vietnam.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/05/cambodia-breaks-ground-on-china-funded-canal-and-says-it-will-be-built-no-matter-the-cost/"  >(SOPHENG CHEANG and ANIRUDDHA GHOSAL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2024-08-06T12:06:12">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2024-08-06T12:06:12">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Reuters, Fast Company">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/06/these-5-states-pushing-elon-musk-fix-xs-chatbot-heres-why.webp" alt="These 5 states are pushing Elon Musk to fix X&#8217;s chatbot. Here&#8217;s why"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">These 5 states are pushing Elon Musk to fix X&#8217;s chatbot. Here&#8217;s why</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Secretaries of state from five U.S. states urged billionaire Elon Musk on Monday to fix social media platform X’s AI chatbot, saying it had spread misinformation related to the Nov. 5 election.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/06/these-5-states-pushing-elon-musk-fix-xs-chatbot-heres-why/"  >(Reuters, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:46:33 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:46:33 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/07/tesla-is-recalling-more-than-1-6-million-cars-in-china-for-a-remote-software-fix.webp" alt="Tesla is recalling more than 1.6 million cars in China for a remote software fix"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tesla is recalling more than 1.6 million cars in China for a remote software fix</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BEIJING (AP) — Tesla is recalling 1.68 million cars in China for a remote software upgrade to ensure that they warn the driver when the trunk is not locked shut, China's market regulator said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/07/tesla-is-recalling-more-than-1-6-million-cars-in-china-for-a-remote-software-fix/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:29:23 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:29:23 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="CIO">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
