           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Team up with HP to power your future of work</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HP sees a future of work where IT plays a more strategic role in business growth. As we accelerate to October 14th, 2025, when Windows 10 support ends, the coming months mark a critical time for many IT Teams.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/05/team-up-with-hp-to-power-your-future-of-work/"  >(CIO)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:53:21 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:53:21 +0000">
