           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Secretaries of state urge Elon Musk to fix AI chatbot spreading election misinformation on X</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      CHICAGO (AP) — Five secretaries of state are urging Elon Musk to fix an AI chatbot on the social media platform X, saying in a letter sent Monday that it has spread election misinformation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/05/secretaries-of-state-urge-elon-musk-to-fix-ai-chatbot-spreading-election-misinformation-on-x/"  >(CHRISTINE FERNANDO, Associated Press, KREX 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
