    <meta itemprop="name" content="HUIZHONG WU, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/01/china-is-restricting-export-of-drones-that-can-be-used-for-military-purposes-and-some-drone-features.webp" alt="China is restricting export of drones that can be used for military purposes and some drone features"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">China is restricting export of drones that can be used for military purposes and some drone features</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BANGKOK (AP) — China will ban the export of all unregulated civilian drones that can be used for military purposes or in terrorist activities and restrict certain drone features as Beijing faces repeated Western criticism for its stance on the Russian invasion of Ukraine.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/01/china-is-restricting-export-of-drones-that-can-be-used-for-military-purposes-and-some-drone-features/"  >(HUIZHONG WU, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
