    <h3 itemprop="headline">Blake Snell tosses Giants' first no-hitter since 2015</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      (KRON) -- San Francisco Giants pitcher Blake Snell threw the team's first no-hitter since 2015 Friday night in Cincinnati. The spectacular outing marked the first win of the season for Snell, who was San Francisco's prized offseason acquisition.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/03/blake-snell-tosses-giants-first-no-hitter-since-2015/"  >(Phil Mayer, KRON4)</a>
