    <h3 itemprop="headline">Pitbull purchases naming rights to FIU Panthers' football stadium</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      FIU announced on Tuesday that international music star Pitbull had purchased the naming rights to their football stadium, making it &quot;Pitbull Stadium&quot; for the next five years.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/06/pitbull-purchases-naming-rights-fiu-panthers-football-stadium/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
