    <h3 itemprop="headline">Utah Jazz preseason schedule announced</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - The Utah Jazz announced their 2024 preseason schedule, which features three home games at Delta Center and three games on the road.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/05/utah-jazz-preseason-schedule-announced/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
