    <h3 itemprop="headline">49ers coach Kyle Shanahan says 'nothing has changed' regarding a trade or a new contract for Aiyuk</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SANTA CLARA, Calif. (AP) — With San Francisco unable to reach a long-term deal with Brandon Aiyuk, the 49ers have given the star receiver permission to talk to other potential suitors.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/06/49ers-coach-kyle-shanahan-says-nothing-has-changed-regarding-a-trade-or-a-new-contract-for-aiyuk/"  >(JOSH DUBOW, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
