           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Understanding Question 3 on the Nevada ballot in the November election</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      More active voters in Nevada identify as non-partisan than Democrat or Republican, and Question 3 on the November ballot might go a long way toward giving them a bigger voice in elections.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/02/understanding-question-3-on-the-nevada-ballot-in-the-november-election/"  >(Greg Haas, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
