  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/07/fox-news-host-knocks-trump-you-either-own-the-markets-or-you-dont.webp" alt="Fox News host knocks Trump: 'You either own the markets or you don&#8217;t'"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Fox News host knocks Trump: 'You either own the markets or you don&#8217;t'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Fox News anchor Neil Cavuto challenged former President Trump’s record and comments on the stock market Monday after the former president blamed President Biden and Vice President Harris for this week's slide.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/07/fox-news-host-knocks-trump-you-either-own-the-markets-or-you-dont/"  >(Nick Robertson, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:00:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:00:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cathy Wurzer, Brian Bakst, Gracie  Stockton, Aleesa Kuznetsov, Megan Burks, and Phil Picardi, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/06/special-coverage-walz-picked-to-run-as-harris-vice-presidential-candidate.webp" alt="Special coverage: Walz picked to run as Harris&#8217; vice presidential candidate"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Special coverage: Walz picked to run as Harris&#8217; vice presidential candidate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tim Walz, the second-term Minnesota governor with a folksy demeanor and a swath of experience inside and out of government, gained a spot on the Democratic ticket as Kamala Harris’ vice presidential choice.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/06/special-coverage-walz-picked-to-run-as-harris-vice-presidential-candidate/"  >(Cathy Wurzer, Brian Bakst, Gracie  Stockton, Aleesa Kuznetsov, Megan Burks, and Phil Picardi, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:27:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:27:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cari Spencer, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/04/rochester-legislator-victim-of-racist-graffiti.webp" alt="Rochester legislator wakes up to racist graffiti at her house"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Rochester legislator wakes up to racist graffiti at her house</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Minnesota Rep. Kim Hicks, DFL-Rochester, woke up to Nazi symbols and racial slurs spray-painted on her home Saturday morning. Hicks is white and her husband is Black. They live with six of their children.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/04/rochester-legislator-victim-of-racist-graffiti/"  >(Cari Spencer, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:00:33 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:00:33 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="ROBERT YOON, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/07/dont-expect-a-balloon-drop-quite-yet-how-the-virtual-roll-call-to-nominate-kamala-harris-will-work.webp" alt="Harris wins Democratic presidential nomination in virtual roll call. Here's how the process worked"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris wins Democratic presidential nomination in virtual roll call. Here's how the process worked</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — Democratic delegates have selected Vice President Kamala Harris to be the party's presidential nominee, according to final vote results released late Monday by the Democratic National Committee. But don't expect a balloon drop just yet.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/07/dont-expect-a-balloon-drop-quite-yet-how-the-virtual-roll-call-to-nominate-kamala-harris-will-work/"  >(ROBERT YOON, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 17:11:31 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 05 Aug 2024 17:11:31 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cathy Wurzer and Ellen Finn, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/05/harris-vp-candidates-narrow-we-talked-to-political-reporters-from-their-home-states.webp" alt="Harris&#8217; VP candidates narrow: We talked to political reporters from their home states"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris&#8217; VP candidates narrow: We talked to political reporters from their home states</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Kamala Harris has narrowed her running mate choices down to three state governors. She is expected to announce who will join her on the Democratic ticket on 
Tuesday morning.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/05/harris-vp-candidates-narrow-we-talked-to-political-reporters-from-their-home-states/"  >(Cathy Wurzer and Ellen Finn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset></main>
